    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs silently and powerful, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic features function exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This car has been meticulously garaged and maintained to the highest standards, making it an ideal choice for a collector or a buyer who demands perfection.",
