    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all weekend warriors and restoration fans! This car is the ultimate project for someone who loves getting their hands dirty. While it requires significant mechanical attention and some major TLC to return to its former glory, it's a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity to build something special from the ground up!",
