      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously preserved specimen, representing the pinnacle of its class. The vehicle remains in superlative condition, featuring an immaculate exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical system has been verified to meet exacting standards, ensuring a refined and reliable driving experience. This is an exceptional acquisition for the discerning buyer who demands a vehicle of distinguished pedigree and flawless presentation.",
