    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total beauty! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garage-kept and detailed regularly. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in truly flawless shape, this is the one. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-pressure VANOS system has been preemptively overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, feeding power to a variable M-differential lock for optimal exit speeds. Finished in its original factory coating with zero paint meter discrepancies, the chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampening. Every component, from the rod bearings to the interior's Nappa leather, reflects a rigorous maintenance protocol. This is a mechanically superlative specimen for the purist collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Full service history. Inspect in person.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in pristine, showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, fully documented service history from authorized dealerships. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It is a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
